{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/compensation/covid-outdoor-schools","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"COVID - Outdoor schools","meta_description":"Dotace pro ubytovací zařízení, která zajišťují pořádání škol v přírodě.","content":{"processed":"<p>The<strong> subsidy</strong> is intended to support accommodation facilities that organize <strong>outdoor schools</strong>.</p>\n<p>Suitable for the subsidy are those facilities that, even after the end of the measure adopted by the government, did not have the opportunity to carry out the contracted stays. </p>\n<h2>Deadlines for the announced call</h2>\n<p><strong>Validity of the call: </strong>November 30th, 2020 - February 12th, 2021.</p>\n<p><strong>Receipt of grant applications:</strong> December 10th, 2020 - February 12th, 2021.</p>\n<p><strong>Decisive period:</strong> May 25th, 2020 - June 29th, 2020.</p>\n<p>You can find the <a href=\"https://zadosti.sfpi.cz\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">electronic application</a> form on the website of the Ministry of Regional Development. </p>\n<p>More information about the program can be found on the <a href=\"https://www.mmr.cz/cs/narodni-dotace/covid-skoly-v-prirode\" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external\">website of the Ministry of Regional Developmen</a>t.</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/compensation/covid-outdoor-schools"},"changed":"2020-12-15T11:15:15+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-30T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2020-12-15T11:15:15+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"money"},"situation_type":{"name":"Compensation","path":{"alias":"/situations/compensation"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"money"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[]},"questions_answers":[],"update":null,"valid_to":"2021-02-12T00:00:00+01:00","last_updated":"2020-12-10T00:00:00+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Compensation","path":{"alias":"/situations/